n and a grinding of black pepper.", "act_image": "https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/30/2021/03/Whole-crispy-roast-chicken-and-asparagus-caesar-0f79829.jpg", "act_nutrients": {"calories": "711 calories", "fatContent": "54 grams fat", "saturatedFatContent": "13 grams saturated fat", "carbohydrateContent": "14 grams carbohydrates", "sugarContent": "3 grams sugar", "fiberContent": "2 grams fiber", "proteinContent": "41 grams protein", "sodiumContent": "1.1 milligram of sodium"}}